  <brief_title>Isomil Post Marketing Observational Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Open-label, Post-marketing Observational Study to Document the Use of Soy-based Infant Formula With Low Chain Polyunsaturates (LCP) in Infants With Symptoms Suggestive to Cow's Milk Allergy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
